    "body" : "<p>Faced similar issue. It's due to java version you are using in docker. If your are using java version 8u291 or later TLS V1.0,1.1 may be disabled. Please check the <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/67742776/docker-container-javax-mail-messagingexception-no-appropriate-protocol-protoco\">Solution</a> here</p>\n"
